## Tone and Style

### Friendly but Professional

- **Friendly**: Use approachable language, avoid overly formal tone
- **Professional**: Maintain clarity and precision
- **Helpful**: Anticipate reader questions and provide clear guidance
- **Concise**: Get to the point without unnecessary words

**Good Examples:**
```markdown
This script makes it easy to query the API and view results.

If you run into issues, check the troubleshooting section below.

You'll need to set up your API key firstâ€”see the setup steps.
```

**Avoid:**
```markdown
It is imperative that users configure the API key prior to execution.

One must ensure that all prerequisites are met before proceeding.

The utilization of this script requires careful attention to detail.
```

