When creating or editing a README, ensure:
- [ ] Starts with a brief overview section (2-3 sentences)
- [ ] Uses clear section headers with appropriate emojis
- [ ] All code blocks include language tags
- [ ] Mermaid diagrams included when documenting workflows/processes
